### POST Request to create a new purchase
POST http://localhost:7071/api/purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "1234",
    "quantity": 1,
    "customerName": "John Doe",
    "customerEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
    "purchasePrice": 100.00
}

###

### GET Request to retrieve purchase information
GET http://localhost:7071/api/purchase?productId=1234&customerName=John Doe

###

### Simple GET Request
GET http://localhost:7071/api/purchase